OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774271469
OL,3,CSearch narrowed for fugitive capybara
OL,4,Cas zoo deploys specialist dog teams
OL,6,FSearch teams are combing water meadows
OL,7,Fnear Twyford after fugitive capybara
OL,8,FSamba was spotted in the area.
OL,10,FMarwell Zoo said on Sunday afternoon
OL,11,Fthat it had received a video of the 9-
OL,12,Fmonth-old in a waterway between
OL,13,FTwyford and the Brambridge Garden
OL,14,Fcentre, around three miles from the
OL,15,Fwildlife park.
OL,17,FSamba went missing on Tuesday after
OL,18,Fshe escaped the temporary enclosure
OL,19,Fshe shared with her sister Tango.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
