CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774271469
OL,3,CSearch narrowed for fugitive capybara
OL,4,Cas zoo deploys specialist dog teams
OL,6,FTango was re-captured within the zoo
OL,7,Fgrounds, but Samba has evaded capture,
OL,8,Fdespite sightings outside the Ship Inn
OL,9,Fin Owslebury on Thursday.
OL,11,FSince then, sniffer dogs and drone
OL,12,Foperators have been out trying to
OL,13,Ftrack the missing rodent, who is the
OL,14,Fsize of a small badger.
OL,16,FCapybaras are intelligent, gentle
OL,17,Fanimals, which do not pose a risk to
OL,18,Fthe public, according to the zoo.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
