PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774271469
OL,3,CSearch narrowed for fugitive capybara
OL,4,Cas zoo deploys specialist dog teams
OL,6,F"Update 13:03pm - our team has
OL,7,Freceived a video of Samba in the
OL,8,Fwaterway between Twyford and
OL,9,FBrambridge Garden Centre. We have
OL,10,Facted immediately, and teams are now
OL,11,Fin the area searching for her.
OL,13,F"We urgently need your help as we
OL,14,Fcontinue to investigate. If you are
OL,15,Fnearby and believe you've seen Samba,
OL,16,Fplease send a photo and exact location
OL,17,Fto 07436 167401.
OL,19,F"Please do not approach Samba.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
