PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774271469
OL,3,CSearch narrowed for fugitive capybara
OL,4,Cas zoo deploys specialist dog teams
OL,6,F"Thank you for your continued support
OL,7,Fwith this ongoing situation, we hope
OL,8,Fto bring Samba home safely very soon."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
